data.description: Exceptional Single-Level Home: 3 Bed, 2 Baths + Office, and 2 Car Garage! Discover the epitome of comfort and style in this immaculate single-level residence. Boasting 3 bedrooms, including a main suite with a main bathroom featuring a walk-in-closet, stand-alone shower, and inviting tub-your personal oasis awaits. The thoughtful design extends to a dedicated office space, perfect for remote work or creative pursuits. Entertain effortlessly in the open-concept living area, complemented by a modern kitchen. Step outside to your own slice of paradise-a spacious backyard offering ample room for relaxation, play, and outdoor gatherings. With a 2-car garage, parking is a breeze, adding to the convenience of this well appointed home.
